# ========================================
# SECURITY NOTE
# ========================================
# This .gitignore file is designed to protect sensitive information
# in the Safe Circle project. Always ensure that:
# 1. No .env files are committed
# 2. No API keys or tokens are hardcoded
# 3. No user data or evidence files are committed
# 4. Secrets are properly managed and rotated regularly
# 5. Use .env.example files to show required environment variables